name: datalakesurfer
summary: A Python package for Azure Datalake Storage adlsgen2 [abfss://] and Microsoft Fabric Lakehouse [abfss://], Google Cloud Storage [gs://bucket], AWS S3 bucket [s3://bucket] enables format detection and schema retrieval for Iceberg, Delta, and Parquet formats.It also helps identify paritioned columns for parquet datasets.
author: Keshav Kant Singh
